\c 14
\s Ukuchithwa kwamaGibhithe oLwandle oluBomvu
\p
\v 1 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhuluma kuMozisi isithi:
\v 2 Tshela abantwana bakoIsrayeli ukuthi baphenduke, bamise inkamba phambi kwePi-Hahirothi\x + 13.18,20; 14.5,9. Nani 33.7,8.\x*, phakathi kweMigidoli lolwandle\x + Jer. 44.1.\x*, phambi kweBhali-Zefoni, maqondana layo limise inkamba elwandle.
\v 3 Njalo uFaro uzakuthi ngabantwana bakoIsrayeli: Badidekile\x + Esta 3.15. Jow. 1.18.\x* elizweni, inkangala ibavalele.
\v 4 Njalo ngizayenza lukhuni inhliziyo kaFaro\x + 7.13.\x*, ukuthi axotshane labo, ngibe sengidunyiswa kuFaro lebuthweni lakhe lonke\x + 9.16; 14.17,18. Roma 9.17,22,23.\x*, ukuze amaGibhithe azi ukuthi ngiyiN\nd kosi\x + 7.5.\x*\nd*. Basebesenza njalo.
\p
\v 5 Kwathi sekubikiwe enkosini yeGibhithe ukuthi abantu babalekile, inhliziyo kaFaro lenhliziyo yenceku zakhe yaguquka mayelana labantu\x + Hlab. 105.25.\x*, basebesithi: Kuyini lokho esikwenzileyo, ukuthi siyekele uIsrayeli ahambe angasisebenzeli?
\v 6 Wasebophela inqola yakhe, wathatha abantu bakhe laye.
\v 7 Wasethatha inqola ezingamakhulu ayisithupha ezikhethiweyo\x + 15.4. Isa. 31.1.\x* lazo zonke inqola zeGibhithe lenduna eziphezu kwazo zonke.
\v 8 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasiyenza lukhuni inhliziyo kaFaro inkosi yeGibhithe\x + 14.4,17; 7.13.\x*, wasexotshana labantwana bakoIsrayeli, kodwa abantwana bakoIsrayeli baphuma ngesandla esiphakemeyo\x + Nani 33.3. 13.9.\x*.
\v 9 Kodwa amaGibhithe asexotshana labo\x + 15.9. Josh. 24.6.\x*, amabhiza wonke, izinqola zikaFaro, labagadi bakhe bamabhiza, lebutho lakhe, abafica bemise inkamba elwandle, eceleni kwePi-Hahirothi phambi kweBhali-Zefoni.
\p
\v 10 Kwathi uFaro esesondele, abantwana bakoIsrayeli baphakamisa amehlo abo, khangela-ke, amaGibhithe ehamba ebalandela, basebesesaba kakhulu. Abantwana bakoIsrayeli basebekhala eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + Josh. 24.7. Neh. 9.9.\x*;
\v 11 bathi kuMozisi\x + Hlab. 106.7,8.\x*: Kungoba kwakungekho mangcwaba yini eGibhithe\x + 2 Kho. 1.3,6,16.\x* ukuthi usithethe ukuze sifele enkangala? Kuyini lokhu okwenze kithi, ukusikhupha eGibhithe?
\v 12 Kayisilo leli ilizwi esalikhuluma kuwe eGibhithe sisithi: Siyekele ukuthi sisebenzele amaGibhithe\x + 5.21; 6.9.\x*? Ngoba bekuzakuba ngcono kithi ukuthi sisebenzele amaGibhithe kulokuthi sifele enkangala.
\v 13 UMozisi wasesithi ebantwini: Lingesabi; manini liqine, libone usindiso lweN\nd kosi\nd* ezalenzela lona lamuhla\x + 2 Lan. 20.15,17. Isa. 41.10,13,14.\x*; ngoba amaGibhithe eliwabonayo lamuhla, kalisayikuwabona futhi kuze kube laphakade.
\v 14 IN\nd kosi\nd* izalilwela\x + 14.25. Dute. 1.30; 3.22; 20.4. Josh. 10.14,42; 23.3. 2 Lan. 20.29. Neh. 4.20. So Isa. 31.4.\x*, lina-ke lizathula\x + 1 Sam. 7.8. Jer. 38.27. Isa. 30.15.\x*.
\p
\v 15 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuMozisi: Ukhalelani kimi? Tshela abantwana bakoIsrayeli ukuthi baqhubekele phambili.
\v 16 Wena-ke, phakamisa intonga yakho, welulele isandla sakho phezu kolwandle\x + 14.26; 7.19.\x* uludabule, ukuze abantwana bakoIsrayeli bahambe phakathi kolwandle emhlabathini owomileyo.
\v 17 Mina-ke, khangela, ngizayenza lukhuni inhliziyo yamaGibhithe\x + 14.4,8.\x* ukuze angene ngemva kwabo. Njalo ngizadunyiswa ngoFaro langebutho lakhe lonke, ngezinqola zakhe, langabagadi bamabhiza bakhe\x + 14.4.\x*.
\v 18 Njalo amaGibhithe azakwazi ukuthi ngiyiN\nd kosi\x + 14.4.\x*\nd* sengidunyiswe ngoFaro, ngezinqola zakhe langabagadi bamabhiza bakhe.
\p
\v 19 Njalo ingilosi kaNkulunkulu\x + Gen. 31.11. 23.20; 32.34. Nani 20.16. Isa. 63.9. Mal. 3.1. 13.21.\x* eyayihamba phambi kwebutho lakoIsrayeli yasuka yayahamba ngemva kwabo; lensika yeyezi yasuka phambi kwabo, yema ngemva kwabo,
\v 20 yasisiza phakathi kwebutho lamaGibhithe lebutho lakoIsrayeli. Njalo yayiliyezi lobumnyama, kodwa yakhanyisa ubusuku, okokuthi elinye kalisondelanga kwelinye ubusuku bonke.
\v 21 UMozisi waseselulela isandla sakhe phezu kolwandle\x + 14.27.\x*; iN\nd kosi\nd* yalwenza ulwandle lwahamba ngomoya olamandla wempumalanga ubusuku bonke, yenza ulwandle lwaba ngumhlabathi owomileyo\x + Hlab. 66.6. Gen. 7.22. Josh. 3.17; 4.18. 2 Kho. 2.8. Hag. 2.6.\x*; amanzi asesehlukaniswa\x + Neh. 9.11. Hlab. 78.13. Isa. 63.12. 15.8. Hlab. 74.13; 106.9; 114.3. Josh. 3.16; 4.23.\x*.
\v 22 Abantwana bakoIsrayeli basebengena olwandle emhlabathini owomileyo\x + 14.29; 15.19. Nani 33.8. Hlab. 66.6. Isa. 63.13. 1 Kor. 10.1. Heb. 11.29. Hlab. 77.17-20.\x*; njalo amanzi aba ngumduli kubo ngakwesokunene sabo langakwesokhohlo sabo.
\p
\v 23 AmaGibhithe asexotshana labo, angena ngemva kwabo, wonke amabhiza kaFaro, inqola zakhe labagadi bamabhiza bakhe, phakathi kolwandle.
\v 24 Kwasekusithi ngomlindo wokusa, iN\nd kosi\nd* yakhangela phansi ebuthweni lamaGibhithe isensikeni yomlilo leyeyezi\x + 1 Sam. 11.11. Hlu. 7.19. Hlab. 63.6; 90.4; 119.148. Lilo 2.19. Mat. 24.43. Mat. 14.25. Mark. 6.48; 13.35. Luka 12.38.\x*, yalidunga ibutho lamaGibhithe;
\v 25 yakhupha amavili ezinqola zawo ukuze zihambe nzima, aze athi amaGibhithe: Asibalekele ubuso bukaIsrayeli, ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* iyabalwela imelene lamaGibhithe\x + 14.14-16.\x*.
\p
\v 26 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuMozisi: Yelulela isandla sakho phezu kolwandle\x + 14.16.\x* ukuze amanzi abuyele phezu kwamaGibhithe, phezu kwenqola zawo laphezu kwabagadi bawo bamabhiza.
\v 27 UMozisi waseselulela isandla sakhe phezu kolwandle\x + 14.21.\x*; ulwandle lwaselubuyela endaweni yalo eyejwayelekileyo\x + Josh. 4.18.\x* emadabukakusa; amaGibhithe asebalekela kulo; iN\nd kosi\nd* yasiwathintithela amaGibhithe phakathi kolwandle\x + 15.1,7. Dute. 11.4. Hlab. 78.53.\x*.
\v 28 Amanzi asebuyela\x + Hab. 3.8-13.\x*, asibekela izinqola labagadi bamabhiza, lebutho lonke likaFaro elalingene olwandle ngemva kwabo; kakusalanga loyedwa kubo\x + Hlab. 106.11.\x*.
\v 29 Kodwa abantwana bakoIsrayeli bahamba phezu komhlabathi owomileyo\x + 14.22.\x* phakathi kolwandle; njalo amanzi aba ngumduli kubo ngakwesokunene sabo langakwesokhohlo sabo.
\v 30 Ngokunjalo iN\nd kosi\nd* yamsindisa uIsrayeli ngalolosuku esandleni samaGibhithe\x + Hlab. 106.8,10.\x*; njalo uIsrayeli wabona amaGibhithe efile ekhunjini lolwandle.
\v 31 UIsrayeli wasebona amandla amakhulu\f + \fk amandla amakhulu: \fl Heb. \fqa isandla esikhulu.\f* iN\nd kosi\nd* eyawenzayo kumaGibhithe. Abantu basebeyesaba iN\nd kosi\nd*, bakholwa eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + 4.31; 19.9. Hlab. 106.12. Joha. 2.11; 11.45.\x*, lakuMozisi inceku yayo.